ABSTRACT
Systems and methods are described for extending coverage
of a wireless device. A plurality of wireless devices located
in a coverage area of a first access node can be monitored for
a first condition. At least one wireless device of the plurality
of wireless devices that meets the first condition can be
classified as a high power wireless device. Two or more
indicators reported by the at least one wireless device are
compared to a criteria. When the two or more indicators
meet the criteria, a handoff of the at least one wireless device
from the first access node to a second access node can be
performed.
